Christopher L. HAMILTON, Petitioner-Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Respondent-Appellee. No. 03-3804. United States Court of Appeals, Seventh Circuit. March 17, 2004. Christopher L. Hamilton, Lompoc, CA, pro se. Colin S. Bruce, Office of the United States Attorney, Urbana, IL, for Respondent-Appellee.

Before BAUER, EASTERBROOK, and KANNE, Circuit Judges.

The court, on its own motion, VACATES the order of March 15, 2004.
